        "timestamp": "2020-05-26 20:10:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nSean,\n\nThank you.\n\nThese are not the retries we need.  This change below loops requests on the same best server and won't progress the cadi request.\n\nInstead, the cadi should back off from this current best aaf server, and pick a second best aaf server.  The first best and second best servers should be different servers.  Retry the request against the second best aaf server.  \n\nJohn",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
